text: Bhavna Jayanty Limbachia (born 21 April 1984) is a British television actress, film, and comedian. She is mainly known for her roles as Alia Khan in Citzen Khan and Rana Habeeb in Coronation Street. She is born in Preston, the city of Lancashire, England. ==References== Category:British actors Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:People from Preston, Lancashire
